components.name: Wait for L2 Full Load Flag
components.description: Polls the md.dwh_flag table in the DWH until the 'l1_to_l2_load_successfull' flag for the previous business day is set.

upstream_policy.description: First task in the pipeline, no upstream dependencies

components.name: Generate Load Identifier
components.description: Creates a unique load identifier for the workflow run and pushes it via XCom for downstream tasks.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after the L2 load flag sensor succeeds

components.name: Register Workflow Session
components.description: Registers the workflow session in metadata tables using the generated load identifier.

components.name: Wait for Previous Day DAG Completion
components.description: Blocks execution until the previous day's run of the same DAG reaches its end task.

components.name: Trigger PostgreSQL Session Cleanup
components.description: Triggers the sys_kill_all_session_pg DAG to clean up PostgreSQL sessions and waits for its completion.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after previousday DAG completion sensor

components.name: Trigger Reporting Data Preparation
components.description: Triggers the wf_data_preparation_for_reports DAG to prepare reporting datasets.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after PostgreSQL session cleanup completes

components.name: Trigger Client Segmentation Load
components.description: Triggers the l1_to_l2_p_load_data_ds_client_segmentation_full DAG to load client segmentation data.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after PostgreSQL session cleanup completes (parallel branch)

components.name: Send Completion Flag to SAP
components.description: Posts a completion flag to the SAP system via HTTP POST after client segmentation data is loaded.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after client segmentation load completes

components.name: Finalize Workflow Session
components.description: Updates metadata tables to mark the workflow session as successful after reporting preparation and SAP notification complete.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after both parallel branches (reporting preparation and SAP flag) have succeeded

components.name: Failure Notification Email
components.description: Sends an email to configured recipients when any upstream task fails.
inputs: failure signals from all upstream tasks

upstream_policy.description: Triggered when any upstream task fails (trigger_rule='one_failed')

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

poke_interval.description: Polling interval in seconds for the SqlSensor

fail_on_empty.description: Whether the sensor should fail if no rows are returned

external_dag_id.description: Identifier of the external DAG to monitor

execution_delta.description: Time delta to look back for the external DAG run (in days)

poke_interval.description: Polling interval in seconds for the ExternalTaskSensor

trigger_dag_id.description: DAG to trigger for PostgreSQL session cleanup

wait_for_completion.description: Whether to wait for the triggered DAG to finish

trigger_dag_id.description: DAG to trigger for reporting data preparation

pool.description: Airflow pool name to limit concurrency

pool_slots.description: Number of slots to consume from the pool

trigger_dag_id.description: DAG to trigger for client segmentation data load

conn_id.description: Connection identifier for the SAP HTTP endpoint

trigger_rule.description: Rule that determines when the email task is triggered

recipients.description: Email address(es) to receive failure notifications

sources: md.dwh_flag table in the PostgreSQL DWH (flag indicating L1toL2 load success)
Completion status of the previous day's WF_MAIN_DATASETS_LOAD_L2_TO_L2 DAG (via ExternalTaskSensor)
Client segmentation source data processed by the external DAG l1_to_l2_p_load_data_ds_client_segmentation_full
sinks: Metadata tables in the DWH (workflow registration and status updates)
SAP system receiving a completion flag via HTTP POST
Failure notification email sent through the SMTP service
intermediate_datasets: Reporting preparation datasets produced by wf_data_preparation_for_reports DAG
ds_client_segmentation_last_v table (row count used for verification)
